            <forecast-period index="0" start-time-local="2026-04-23T15:00:00+09:30" end-time-local="2026-04-24T00:00:00+09:30" start-time-utc="2026-04-23T05:30:00Z" end-time-utc="2026-04-23T14:30:00Z">
                <text type="forecast">Clear. Winds east to northeasterly 15 to 20 km/h becoming light in the evening.</text>
            </forecast-period>
            <forecast-period index="1" start-time-local="2026-04-24T00:00:00+09:30" end-time-local="2026-04-25T00:00:00+09:30" start-time-utc="2026-04-23T14:30:00Z" end-time-utc="2026-04-24T14:30:00Z">
                <text type="forecast">Mostly sunny. Light winds becoming north to northeasterly 15 to 25 km/h in the morning. Overnight temperatures falling to around 8 with daytime temperatures reaching the high 20s.</text>
                <text type="fire_danger">Moderate</text>
                <text type="uv_alert">Sun protection 9:50am to 2:10pm, UV Index predicted to reach 4 [Moderate]</text>
            </forecast-period>
            <forecast-period index="2" start-time-local="2026-04-25T00:00:00+09:30" end-time-local="2026-04-26T00:00:00+09:30" start-time-utc="2026-04-24T14:30:00Z" end-time-utc="2026-04-25T14:30:00Z">
                <text type="forecast">Mostly sunny. Slight chance of a shower in the west in the evening. Near zero chance of rain elsewhere. The chance of a thunderstorm in the west at night. Winds north to northeasterly 15 to 20 km/h tending north to northwesterly 20 to 30 km/h in the morning then becoming light in the late evening. Overnight temperatures falling to around 12 with daytime temperatures reaching the low 30s.</text>
            </forecast-period>
            <forecast-period index="3" start-time-local="2026-04-26T00:00:00+09:30" end-time-local="2026-04-27T00:00:00+09:30" start-time-utc="2026-04-25T14:30:00Z" end-time-utc="2026-04-26T14:30:00Z">
                <text type="forecast">Medium chance of showers, most likely in the morning. Mostly sunny afternoon. Light winds becoming southwesterly 15 to 20 km/h during the morning then tending southerly during the afternoon. Overnight temperatures falling to around 13 with daytime temperatures reaching the low to mid 20s.</text>
            </forecast-period>
            <forecast-period index="4" start-time-local="2026-04-27T00:00:00+09:30" end-time-local="2026-04-28T00:00:00+09:30" start-time-utc="2026-04-26T14:30:00Z" end-time-utc="2026-04-27T14:30:00Z">
                <text type="forecast">The chance of morning fog. Sunny afternoon. Light winds. Overnight temperatures falling to around 9 with daytime temperatures reaching the mid 20s.</text>
            </forecast-period>
        </area>
